Here I store various configuration files to quickly set up the environment.
To start:

1. clone/download the repository to `$HOME/code/personal/dotfiles`
2. checkout the submodules as well: `git submodule update --init --recursive`
3. download and install Dropbox. Sync the folder `workspace`.
3. run the bootstrap script: `/bin/bash $HOME/code/personal/dotfiles/bootstrap.sh`
